{
  "stem": "24195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were really in a-- in an overwhelming mood of victory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, it was so-- it seemed like that nothing is going to stop Germany from, from winning this war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was actually before the US really entered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The US didn't enter until, you know--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--after--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--December.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember it, as, again, as another thing that the-- another optimistic event for Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, now, Japan is in the war with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the Axis-- Germany-- Nazi Germany, Fascist Italy, and now Japan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's going to mean that those three nations are going to win this war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was certainly an unpleasant time for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I wanted to learn and benefit as much as I could from, from, from an education.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was almost made impossible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, take-- everybody in my-- this was an all-- I went to a high school that was a public school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't-- and no coeds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was all males.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Hohenzollern Oberschule, H-O-H-E-N-Z-O-L-L-E-R-N Oberschule, which means gymnasium, you know, high school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everyone in this class was a-- was a member of the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to join the Hitler Youth movement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a junior group, like the, the little Boy Scouts, where we-- at six--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cub Scouts.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cub Scouts, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now-- and then you have to-- and then you move up to regular scouts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were-- so we were what, 14, 15 years olds-- 13, 14, 15.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- these were the regular-- these were members of the regular Hitler Youth movement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were all wearing brown shirts with an-- a swastika armband and then summer shorts, brown shorts, and, of course, in the winter, long pants.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
